  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    id="faq"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Is AboutC2PA compatible with all platforms?',
        description:
          'Yes, AboutC2PA is designed to work seamlessly across multiple platforms, including web, Android, iOS, and more. Its SDK ensures smooth integration, allowing you to use it in your preferred environment without limitations.',
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-right',
      },
      {
        title: 'Can I use AboutC2PA for both personal and commercial purposes?',
        description: `Certainly! AboutC2PA is flexible and can be used for personal and commercial projects alike. Whether you're a content creator protecting your work or an enterprise ensuring content authenticity, AboutC2PA has the tools to meet your needs.`,
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-right',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do I need advanced technical knowledge to use AboutC2PA?',
        description:
          'Not at all! AboutC2PA’s intuitive interface and SDK make it easy to get started, even for users with limited technical expertise. For developers and advanced users, AboutC2PA offers extensive customization options to fit complex workflows.',
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-right',
      },
      {
        title: 'Does AboutC2PA require me to upload my content to the server?',
        description: `No, AboutC2PA ensures your content remains secure by not requiring uploads to its server. All signing processes occur locally, preventing any risk of content leakage or unintended exposure.`,
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-right',
      },
      {
        title: 'What are the differences between the free and paid versions of AboutC2PA?',
        description: `The free version allows you to use one signing key issued by About Service Inc. with a fixed signer identity. The paid version offers advanced features, including multiple signing keys, customizable signing identities, and tailored management for diverse signing needs.`,
        icon: 'tabler:chevrons-right',
      },
      {
        title: 'Is customer support available for AboutC2PA users?',
        description: `Absolutely! Our dedicated customer support team is available to assist with any questions, technical issues, or guidance needed to maximize your use of AboutC2PA. Feel free to contact us anytime through our support channels.`,
